# Generated, committed artifacts. They must stay in the tree (//go:embed
# resolves them at compile time and `go install` has no generate step),
# but they're derived from a source of truth - never hand-edit them, run
# `make generate`. linguist-generated folds them in GitHub diffs and drops
# them from language stats so a derived-file diff isn't mistaken for a
# source change. eol=lf keeps the go:embed'd corpora LF on every platform:
# without it a Windows (autocrlf) checkout bakes CRLF into the binary, and the
# `rad docs` snapshot tests then fail on the line-ending mismatch.
core/embedded_docs/**                 linguist-generated=true text eol=lf
rts/embedded_funcs/**                 linguist-generated=true text eol=lf
rts/embedded/functions.txt            linguist-generated=true text eol=lf
rts/signatures_gen.go                 linguist-generated=true
docs-web/docs/reference/functions.md  linguist-generated=true
docs-web/docs/reference/errors.md     linguist-generated=true
